{"tid":289443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[天冇眼] 獲撤破產呈請 梅媽呻每月9萬元生活費唔夠用","createTime":"2017-06-19T04:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T04:20:10.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3384167fe6d95a6732173035850329d7392c143","tid":289443,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:19:12.000Z","msg":"去年4月才解除破產令的「梅媽」覃美金，因欠下2名破產案中的產業受託人10萬元訟費，今年3月遭對方呈請破產，梅媽反駁指是對方將其銀行戶口凍結，才未能還款。案件今提訊時，兩名債權人代表律師今指梅媽已還清欠款，向法庭申請撤銷破產呈請，獲法庭批准，本案訟費將留待聆案官另作處理。<br />\n<br />\n梅媽於庭外透露，還清了十多萬訟費後，本案的訟費仍未處理，大呻：「唔係我搞佢哋，係佢哋搞我。」<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>又提到每月只得約9萬元生活費太少，需要租屋及聘請工人等等。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"93b46c34420101032e140801a6b690eacee78d87","tid":289443,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:19:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170619/56847428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170619%2F56847428&d=zGjnhggtEuWaQdY2yEmPV5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c460e50a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170619%2F56847428&h=6cb9ff31\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170619/56847428</a>"},{"pid":"7deab79ce1e81bb0503738b48aa77005b82789ef","tid":289443,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:20:10.000Z","msg":"好耐之前有篇講佢每月支出  <br />\n養狗  不包括梅XX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}